arts.ttl: Jeffrey De Lange to start for Marseille against Le Havre
arts.sum: Roberto De Zerbi has confirmed his intention to rotate his Marseille squad ahead of Saturday night’s Ligue 1 fixture against Le Havre (21:05 CET), with Dutch goalkeeper Jeffrey De Lange…

Marseille are on a run of four wins in a row, but they still sit behind Paris Saint-Germain in the league table. They've won five of their opening seven league matches, scoring 15 goals in the process...
